    Class Description
    BillChocAn
    BillChocAn serves as a framework that a provider can utilize to BillChocAn.
    DateTime
    DateTime is able to store and return dates and times.
    EFT
    EFT accepts an ArrayList of type TransactionRecord, sorts the array, and then traverses the array, making necessary output for the EFT.
    Manager
    The Manager class implements the manager.
    Member
    The Manager class implements the abstract base class User.
    MemberRecords
    The MemberRecords class implements the class which contains the member records.
    MemberReport
    MemberReport outputs the report of a member's transactions to file.
    Operator
    Operator creates a framework that an operator can use to add/remove and update members/providers.
    Provider
    The Provider class implements the abstract base class User.
    ProviderRecords
    The ProviderRecords class implements the class that contains the member records It contains the setters, getters, for the field provider, which is of type provider, it also includes getters for the fields size and recordIndex, which is are ints.
    ProviderReport
    ProviderReport outputs the report of a provider's transactions to file.
    Service
    The Service class implements the service provided to a member.
    SummaryReport
    SummaryReport accepts an ArrayList of type TransactionRecord, sorts the array, and then traverses the array, making necessary output for the SummaryReport.
    Terminal
    Main method that runs the provider/operator/manager terminal.
    TransactionRecord
    TransactionRecords creates a record of each transaction that a provider provides to a specified member, which contains the current date, date of service, provider, member, service, and any additional comments.
    WeeklyMaintenance
    WeeklyMaintenance performs weekly maintenance by printing a number of various reports upon a timer reaching Friday at midnight.
